27
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,260
Aren't you surprised?

28
00:02:04,620 --> 00:02:05,500
What a huge surprise.

29
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:08,740
What are you doing at Ling'an?

30
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:11,180
I've been upholding justice

31
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:12,460
