33
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:16,740
Maybe it's because I sensed

34
00:02:16,740 --> 00:02:17,900
that you needed me.

35
00:02:18,300 --> 00:02:19,780
Indeed. When I met Long Dan,

36
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:20,980
I heard that you were seriously wounded.

37
00:02:21,820 --> 00:02:23,020
Let me see. Where were you hurt?

38
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:26,180
Let go!

39
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,140
Chuchu.

40
00:02:30,140 --> 00:02:31,060
It's been so many years.

41
00:02:31,980 --> 00:02:32,740
Can't you behave

42
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:33,780
