45
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:46,660
of gender segregation?

46
00:02:47,020 --> 00:02:48,220
By being married off and shipped away?

47
00:02:53,300 --> 00:02:54,060
I know now.

48
00:02:55,020 --> 00:02:56,900
I'm sure you came here to hide
because your family

49
