since I was passing by.

59
00:03:22,980 --> 00:03:24,340
You mean Qi?

60
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:25,260
He's inside.

61
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:25,900
I'll take you inside.

62
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:28,100
Are you two old acquaintances?

63
00:03:28,579 --> 00:03:29,660
We're more than that.

64
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:30,860
My father was in the military as well.

65
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:32,180
We grew up together.

66
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:33,900
We even had

67
