83
00:03:59,540 --> 00:04:00,340
Sure. Let's go.

84
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:02,980
Qi.

85
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:04,900
Miss Jiang is here to visit you.

86
00:04:08,380 --> 00:04:08,900
Commandant Yu.

87
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:10,060
Miss Jiang, please have a seat.

88
