116
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:02,500
I didn't intend to stay for long.

117
00:05:02,660 --> 00:05:03,100
But since I met

118
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:04,420
Qi and Long Dan here,

119
00:05:04,740 --> 00:05:06,140
I think I'll stay for a few more days.

120
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:07,900
Qi, I'm not troubling you, aren't I?

121
00:05:11,540 --> 00:05:12,220
Not at all.

122
00:05:14,380 --> 00:05:15,180
Great.

123
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:15,940
That means

124
00:05:15,940 --> 00:05:16,580
