128
00:05:22,340 --> 00:05:23,260
- with my medicine.
- Medicine?

129
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:23,900
Give it to me.

130
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:25,620
Miss Jiang, sorry for the trouble.

131
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:26,180
Not at all.

132
