144
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:18,020
By the way,

145
00:06:18,620 --> 00:06:20,580
Mr. Yu, what would you like
to have tomorrow?

146
00:06:22,140 --> 00:06:22,740
Delicious.

147
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:24,860
