148
00:06:34,420 --> 00:06:37,220
[Princess Royal's Mansion]

149
00:06:55,740 --> 00:06:58,620
[Rong Yang, Princess Royal of Zhou]

150
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:01,140
Mother.

151
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:02,260
