169
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:34,580
Even so, he tried
to ask for my hands back then.

170
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:36,460
Mingyue,

171
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:39,380
I've told you this many times.

172
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:42,340
You need to show
the Marquis some respect.

173
00:07:43,180 --> 00:07:45,780
During the invasion of Nanwu,

174
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:47,780
he and your father

175
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,260
protected our realm
together with their men.

176
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:51,900
Not only has he contributed
to the peace of the realm,

177
00:07:54,020 --> 00:07:56,500
but I'm also indebted to him.

178
00:07:57,940 --> 00:07:58,780
So Mother,

179
00:07:58,820 --> 00:08:00,540
how do you intend to rescue Cao Xingyu?

180
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,380
What solution do you have?

181
00:08:10,380 --> 00:08:12,100
Mother, you should make an appearance

182
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:13,100
as the Princess Royal.

183
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:15,380
I bet the Capital Administration Office
will release him.

184
00:08:16,060 --> 00:08:17,220
The victims

185
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:18,780
were just girls from humble backgrounds.

186
00:08:19,460 --> 00:08:20,340
Just give their family

187
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:21,860
a hefty sum of compensation fee,

188
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:23,300
and the issue

189
00:08:23,540 --> 00:08:24,740
will be resolved.

190
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:26,580
How did you come up with that idea?

191
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:29,220
Aren't I intelligent?

192
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:32,500
You're too naive for your own good.

193
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:34,539
In the future,

194
00:08:34,659 --> 00:08:36,580
I have to ask your uncle

195
00:08:36,659 --> 00:08:38,860
to find you the best man in the world.

196
00:08:39,179 --> 00:08:40,059
And, I have to

197
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:41,179
test him first.

198
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:42,940
I can only rest at ease

199
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:45,220
once he passes the test.

200
00:08:46,780 --> 00:08:47,540
Mother, you're the best.

201
00:08:51,420 --> 00:08:52,140
His Lordship requests an audience.

202
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:54,540
My Lord.

203
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:02,260
Your Highness.

204
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:05,340
This treasure is known
as the Golden Plant.

205
00:09:05,860 --> 00:09:07,620
The branches are made of pure gold.

206
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:09,780
The flowers, pure white nephrite.

207
00:09:10,180 --> 00:09:12,580
And the leaves, top-quality jadeite.

208
00:09:13,020 --> 00:09:14,820
I went to great lengths

209
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:16,180
to obtain it from Lingnan.

210
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,820
I'm here to present it
to you, Your Highness.

211
00:09:19,180 --> 00:09:20,420
You came here
in the middle of the night.

212
00:09:21,420 --> 00:09:22,900
I suppose you're here for your son.

213
00:09:23,780 --> 00:09:25,540
Your Highness, you're wise indeed.

214
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:27,220
Zhen Heng
of the Capital Administration Office

215
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:29,060
and the new commandant, Yu Qi,

216
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:31,140
