and show no regard for others.

217
00:09:31,220 --> 00:09:33,100
They don't respect me at all.

218
00:09:33,300 --> 00:09:34,460
They came up

219
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:35,940
with a ridiculous excuse

220
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:37,780
to send my son to prison.

221
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:38,940
