to sentence him to death as well!

222
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:39,600
Your Highness.

223
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,150
You must uphold justice for me!

224
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:44,220
Did you make up this charge?

225
00:09:44,340 --> 00:09:45,180
Or is it true?

226
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,030
Your Highness.

227
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,390
Every word I utter is true.

228
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:50,240
I dare not make up such charges!

229
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:52,790
Your Highness, as you know,

230
00:09:53,270 --> 00:09:57,390
I only have one son!

231
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,960
You want me to help you out,

232
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,550
yet you're not telling me the truth.

233
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,480
How can I help you out?

234
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,030
I...

