[Main Hall
of the Capital Administration Office]

236
00:11:05,660 --> 00:11:05,980
Chief.

237
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,180
Chief, how is your arm?

238
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:08,700
It's healed.

239
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:10,140
Take a look at this.

240
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:12,540
When we were searching
the Marquis of Changxing's Mansion,

241
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:13,700
not only did we find whips

242
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,340
in the secret chamber,

243
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:15,740
but we also found this.

244
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:18,460
I've asked Miss Chi about this.

245
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:20,180
Cao Xingyu calls this drug

246
00:11:20,260 --> 00:11:22,060
Divine Bliss.

247
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:24,420
He'd take one pill

248
00:11:24,500 --> 00:11:26,300
before he started abusing his victims.

249
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:27,620
This drug is...

250
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:28,340
Open it!

251
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:33,060
This drug

252
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:34,460
is the real deal.

253
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:44,780
How did he swallow this?

254
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:45,940
Go and ask a physician

255
00:11:45,980 --> 00:11:47,340
if he has some sort of chronic illness.

256
00:11:47,820 --> 00:11:49,060
I've done the inquiry.

257
00:11:49,340 --> 00:11:49,700
He...

258
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:55,140
You see, this drug is...

259
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:56,580
