260
00:11:58,500 --> 00:11:59,300
It's an aphrodisiac.

261
00:12:03,060 --> 00:12:04,540
The key is that the main ingredient

262
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:06,020
is a plant called Pueraria lobata.

263
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:07,020
Such plants

264
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:08,220
are only found in Nanwu.

265
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:09,740
The physician said

266
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:11,740
he only saw these plants

267
00:12:11,780 --> 00:12:12,500
when Zhou and Nanwu

268
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,420
were still

269
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:14,340
open for trade.

270
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:16,260
They've been banned for ages.

271
00:12:23,540 --> 00:12:24,940
Seems like Cao Xingyu has committed

272
00:12:25,340 --> 00:12:27,460
more than just murder.

273
00:12:28,780 --> 00:12:29,940
I was anxious about not having any leads.

274
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:31,580
And then he just hands them over.

275
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:33,460
Report!

276
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:35,180
Mr. Yu!

277
00:12:35,620 --> 00:12:36,260
Mr. Zhen!

278
00:12:36,380 --> 00:12:37,780
Outside...

279
00:12:37,900 --> 00:12:38,860
Hurry and check it out!

280
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:42,980
Who are the Gale Guards?

281
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:44,780
They're
under His Majesty's direct command.

282
00:12:45,420 --> 00:12:47,300
They investigate public sentiment
and oversee all officials.

283
00:12:47,860 --> 00:12:49,540
They have more power
than the Capital Administration Office.

284
00:12:51,020 --> 00:12:52,020
The one who's visiting us today

285
