00:12:58,660 --> 00:12:59,580
Mr. Han!

288
00:13:03,660 --> 00:13:04,180
Mr. Han.

289
00:13:04,530 --> 00:13:06,760
[Han Ran, Commander of the Gale Guards]

290
00:13:06,940 --> 00:13:07,780
Your Lordship,

291
00:13:08,460 --> 00:13:10,900
Her Highness sent me with this message.

292
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,800
She's aware of the matter

293
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:13,820
of the Capital Administration Office.

294
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,440
Please don't worry.

295
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:17,270
Her Highness said

296
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,510
you're a distinguished general
of the realm.

297
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:22,000
By helping you, Her Highness
is also helping our realm.

298
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,390
Her Highness also said

299
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,510
that after this incident,

300
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:26,910
your son cannot stay

301
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,870
at Ling'an any longer.

302
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:35,600
Relay my message to Her Highness.

303
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:36,670
I'll send

304
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,200
that unfilial son of mine
somewhere far away.

305
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,480
He shall never set foot
in Ling'an again.

306
00:13:41,030 --> 00:13:42,390
[Main Hall]
I came here today

307
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:44,600
[of the Capital Administration Office]
to demand an individual

308
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,320
from you.

309
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:46,960
Who is it?

310
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:48,910
The Marquis of Changxing's
heir apparent,

311
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,750
Cao Xingyu.

312
00:13:53,150 --> 00:13:53,790
This person

313
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:55,200
is a major criminal
of the Capital Administration Office.

314
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:56,670
The case hasn't been solved yet.

315
00:13:57,390 --> 00:13:58,320
Pardon us for not being able to comply.

316
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,480
What a coincidence.

317
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,600
Cao Xingyu

318
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:03,910
is also related to a case

319
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:05,390
that the Gale Guards
have been investigating

320
00:14:05,390 --> 00:14:06,360
for many years.

321
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:11,360
And, it's a major case related
to collusion with Nanwu.

322
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,030
Mr. Han,

323
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,240
do you have the official documents?

324
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,000
There are just a few sentences.

325
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:28,670
And, they're not detailed.

326
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:30,720
I'm afraid it's not convincing enough.

327
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:34,000
Commandant Yu, you just assumed
your position not long ago.

328
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:35,510
I suppose you have no idea.

329
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:37,390
The cases
that the Gale Guards investigate

330
00:14:37,670 --> 00:14:39,080
are confidential cases
of the imperial court.

331
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:40,960
As for the details of the cases,

332
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:43,030
they're confidential.

333
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:44,960
All right.

334
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,480
I'm a busy man.

335
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:48,670
Please

336
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:51,120
bring Cao Xingyu here
as soon as possible

337
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,240
and hand him to me.

338
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:54,320
Cao Xingyu

339
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:57,440
is suspected
of taking more than ten lives.

340
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,030
His sin is unpardonable.

341
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:01,320
The Capital Administration Office
hasn't even closed the case yet,

342
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:03,750
but you want to take him with you

343
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:05,720
by saying
that your case is confidential?

344
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:06,840
If so,

345
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:09,910
please pardon us for not being
able to cooperate with you.

346
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,600
Although the Gale Guards
follow His Majesty's order,

347
00:15:12,790 --> 00:15:15,910
the Capital Administration Office
are handling major cases too.

348
00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:17,000
Everything

349
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:19,270
must follow the order of precedence.

350
00:15:19,510 --> 00:15:21,840
Since we arrested him first,

351
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:24,910
we should be the ones
conducting the trial.

352
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:36,150
Miss Chi is safe here.

353
00:15:36,670 --> 00:15:37,320
Don't worry.

354
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:40,510
I've heard
about the Gale Guards visiting you all

355
00:15:40,510 --> 00:15:41,240
this afternoon.

356
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:42,720
Thank you for that.

357
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,030
This matter

358
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,390
has truly caused you trouble, huh?

359
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:54,910
It's nothing.

360
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:58,440
I just didn't expect someone
to rat me out.

361
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:01,270
Miss Chi is inside.

362
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:02,550
Go on in.

363
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,000
I won't join you.

364
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,790
Okay. I'll go and check on her, then.

365
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:14,030
Come here.

366
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,510
Regarding the matter this afternoon,

367
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:17,510
Aman was the one...

368
00:16:17,630 --> 00:16:19,240
Have you obtained
the documents from Han Ran?

369
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:30,080
Take some rest. I'll do it.

370
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,510
I can't just rest here.

371
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:35,600
By the way, Miss Chi,

372
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,200
do you need to write

373
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:38,750
to your family first?

374
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:39,790
No need for that.

375
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,360
I don't have any kin.

376
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:43,870
I was an orphan since young.

377
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,630
My brother and his wife took me in.

378
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:47,440
However,

379
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:49,840
they sold me off to a pleasure house.

380
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:51,600
Miss Si, you have no idea.

381
00:16:51,750 --> 00:16:53,360
They don't care about kinship at all.

382
00:16:53,670 --> 00:16:55,750
Their minds are only filled
with their own interests.

383
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,590
Right after I settled down
in the outskirts,

384
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:00,590
they rushed here overnight

385
00:17:01,350 --> 00:17:02,590
upon hearing about it.

386
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,160
I thought

387
00:17:04,790 --> 00:17:07,240
they felt terrible for me.

388
00:17:08,589 --> 00:17:09,200
In the end...

389
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:12,069
I was such a fool.

390
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:15,240
I shouldn't have had
any expectations of them.

391
00:17:15,680 --> 00:17:16,880
What did you say?

392
00:17:17,349 --> 00:17:18,400
You want me

393
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,680
to be Cao Xingyu's concubine?

394
00:17:23,069 --> 00:17:24,030
Shuying,

395
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:26,310
given your condition,

396
00:17:26,790 --> 00:17:28,160
who else do you think
you can get married to?

397
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:31,790
We're talking about
the Marquis of Changxing's Mansion here.

398
00:17:33,030 --> 00:17:34,550
The betrothal gifts they sent us

399
00:17:35,350 --> 00:17:36,830
had filled our entire courtyard,
you know?

400
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,070
Even the marriage

401
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,640
between your brother and I

402
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,880
wasn't as glorious as such.

403
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:42,160
Once you marry into their family,

404
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,400
no one dares to gossip

405
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:45,750
or talk bad about you.

406
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:49,070
We're doing this for your own good.

407
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:50,640
Seriously?

408
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,480
Our parents entrusted me to you

409
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,310
before they passed away.

410
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:03,750
What? Was it not enough

411
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:06,880
for you to sell me off
to a pleasure house?

412
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:11,000
Now, you're trying to kick me
into another abyss?

413
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:12,070
Back then,

414
00:18:12,110 --> 00:18:13,640
I had no choice either.

415
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,200
An opportunity

416
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:15,680
is staring you in the face.

417
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:17,880
I just want you to lead a good life.

418
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,270
Now that I think about it,

419
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:23,310
ever since the day

420
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:24,240
they sold me off to the pleasure house,

421
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:25,400
my family

422
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:27,400
no longer exists.

423
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:28,880
Miss Chi,

424
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:30,640
although you've escaped from danger,

425
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,750
you're still willing to risk your life

426
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:33,960
to save other people.

427
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:36,270
With your courage and resilience,

428
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,110
I'm sure you can overcome all obstacles.

429
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:40,400
You taught me that.

430
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:41,920
Miss Jiang,

431
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,880
you rescued me
without expecting anything in return.

432
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,350
I'll surely follow your ways.

433
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,200
When other people are in trouble,

434
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,920
I'll lend them a hand.

435
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:49,640
Don't worry.

436
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:51,440
We have Commandant Yu
and Mr. Zhen with us.

437
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,440
The truth

438
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:54,200
will be brought to light.

439
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:57,960
Thank you, Miss Jiang.

440
00:18:58,380 --> 00:19:02,980
[Capital Administration Office]

441
00:19:04,590 --> 00:19:05,350
Cao Xingyu.

442
00:19:06,510 --> 00:19:08,110
Do you intend

443
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,680
to keep pretending to be mute?

444
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,350
You should open your eyes
and take a look.

445
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:14,960
We found this

446
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:18,030
in your study.

447
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:20,400
It's called Divine Bliss, right?

448
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:28,750
What is that?

449
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,480
I've never heard of it before.

450
00:19:30,550 --> 00:19:32,160
Is that so?

451
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,590
I suppose you didn't use it, then.

452
00:19:37,030 --> 00:19:39,070
Don't tell me your father
was the one using it.

453
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,110
Shut up!

454
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,160
Fine. I'll shut up.

455
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:44,830
His father is pretty old.

456
00:19:44,830 --> 00:19:45,550
I never expected him to use this.

457
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:45,960
My goodness.

458
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:46,400
Yu Qi!

459
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:47,200
Fine.

460
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:48,240
I won't bring it up.

461
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:50,830
Let's talk about something else.

462
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:55,030
The formula came

463
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:57,400
from Nanwu, right?

464
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,830
I never expected

465
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:03,400
the Marquis of Changxing's family

466
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:05,310
to collude with Nanwu

467
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:07,680
and betray our realm.

468
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:10,720
Yu Qi.

469
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:12,830
Listen up.

470
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:14,920
Stop trying to slander my family.

471
00:20:17,510 --> 00:20:19,400
You said you found this
in my study, huh?

472
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:21,480
I can say that you're framing me!

473
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:22,880
Excellent.

474
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:24,920
I can rest at ease

475
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,000
when you're showing me that reaction.

476
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,030
I trust you.

477
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,240
Show it to him.

478
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:34,220
[Cao Xingyu, heir apparent
to the Marquis of Changxing,]

479
00:20:34,220 --> 00:20:35,460
[has colluded with Nanwu]

480
00:20:37,680 --> 00:20:38,440
What does this mean?

481
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:41,880
Being locked up in prison,

482
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:42,960
you're naturally cut off
from information.

483
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:47,270
Just now, the Gale Guards were here.

484
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:50,070
They wanted to take you with them

485
00:20:50,070 --> 00:20:51,030
under the crime of collusion with Nanwu.

486
00:20:51,550 --> 00:20:52,720
Cao Xingyu

487
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:54,960
murdered individuals
and buried their bodies

488
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:57,920
because he was
under the control of Nanwu.

489
00:20:58,720 --> 00:20:59,400
Nanwu?

490
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:00,680
According to

491
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:01,920
our years of investigation,

492
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,750
the people of Nanwu have sent their men

493
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,030
to infiltrate Ling'an City

494
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,640
and establish the Nightingale Sect

495
00:21:07,030 --> 00:21:08,880
to approach high-ranking officials

496
00:21:09,270 --> 00:21:12,030
to gather intel
and seek opportunities for subversion.

497
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:15,110
The Marquis of Changxing
is the top general of our realm.

498
00:21:15,790 --> 00:21:17,750
He holds a high position
in the military.

499
00:21:18,030 --> 00:21:19,680
He also guards the imperial city.

500
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:21,750
They tempted him several times

501
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,400
but to no avail.

502
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:25,070
That's why they shifted their focus

503
00:21:25,070 --> 00:21:27,000
to his son, Cao Xingyu.

504
00:21:27,110 --> 00:21:28,480
They controlled him by using drugs,

505
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:29,920
forcing him to commit murder.

506
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:32,110
If they could use the drug

507
00:21:32,830 --> 00:21:34,750
to control Cao Xingyu,

508
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:38,110
why didn't they control
his father directly?

509
00:21:41,590 --> 00:21:42,400
This is the Nanwu people's

510
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,160
counterintelligence plot.

511
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:45,110
Their goal

512
00:21:45,510 --> 00:21:47,440
is to drive a wedge
between the Marquis of Changxing

513
00:21:48,030 --> 00:21:49,590
and His Majesty.

514
00:21:53,030 --> 00:21:53,550
What's wrong?

515
00:21:55,030 --> 00:21:57,270
The Gale Guards
are trying to arrest this person.

516
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,160
Do you think you can keep him

517
00:21:59,160 --> 00:22:00,160
from us by force?

518
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:01,200
Today,

519
00:22:01,790 --> 00:22:02,550
you

520
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:04,440
have to hand Cao Xingyu over

521
00:22:04,750 --> 00:22:05,680
by hook or by crook.

522
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:06,550
I won't!

523
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:07,830
Do you dare to steal him from us?

524
00:22:08,790 --> 00:22:10,440
Aren't you afraid
that I might report you

525
00:22:10,550 --> 00:22:11,550
to His Majesty?

526
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:12,270
Go ahead.

527
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:16,510
Hurry up.

528
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:19,550
If you can bring

529
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:20,960
His Majesty's edict here,

530
00:22:21,400 --> 00:22:21,860
you

531
00:22:22,540 --> 00:22:23,100
can take him with you.

532
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,140
If not,

533
00:22:24,660 --> 00:22:25,660
don't even think about it.

534
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:26,680
Three days.

535
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:30,000
You have three days.

536
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:31,640
You had no idea

537
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:33,350
how much I did

538
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:34,640
in order to keep you here.

539
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:37,480
You should know

540
00:22:38,790 --> 00:22:39,960
what consequences await you

541
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:40,830
if they get their hands

542
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:42,920
on such evidence.

543
00:22:51,110 --> 00:22:52,030
What do you want?

544
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,680
It's not about me.

545
00:22:54,590 --> 00:22:57,110
It's about how you intend
to give me an account.

546
00:22:57,960 --> 00:23:00,480
Where did you get the drugs?

547
00:23:01,180 --> 00:23:03,860
[Base of Nightingale Sect]

548
00:23:23,220 --> 00:23:27,540
[Sang Qi, a spy of Nightingale Sect]

549
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,960
The Saintess brings glory to Nanwu.

550
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:54,550
Du'er, you summoned me
in the middle of the night.

551
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,220
Did something happen?

552
00:23:56,220 --> 00:23:58,620
[Du'er, Leader of Nightingale Sect]

553
00:23:58,830 --> 00:23:59,790
The case of
the Marquis of Changxing's Mansion

554
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,550
has been causing quite a stir
these past two days.

555
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:02,920
I heard

556
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,720
that they even found leads
that were related to Nanwu.

557
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:07,830
You were in charge
of keeping an eye on their family.

558
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,160
What happened?

559
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,070
Du'er, here's the thing.

560
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:14,160
Cao Xingyu is a lecherous man.

561
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:15,830
I wanted to use that to our advantage

562
00:24:16,110 --> 00:24:17,640
and make him a pawn of our sect.

563
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,720
He was supposed
to be our new pawn in Ling'an.

564
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:23,110
I never expected him to be so foolish.

565
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:24,440
After he had tortured

566
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,550
and murdered over ten girls,

567
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:26,400
